		<div id="comment_body_64466515"><p>Between Return To Office, then outsourcing teams offshore, and now not giving raise despite huge profits, Google has completely graduated into your run-of-the-mill giant mature faceless and heartless corporation.</p><p>It is futile to hope the execs care about employee morale, execs in a mature corps only care about getting money into their own pocket and nothing else.</p></div>
	</div>

